{"tid":2317053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【好鄰舍教會：10 警員搜觀塘會址　社工劉家棟稱被帶走助查】","createTime":"2020-12-08T09:41:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T11:31:22.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e3c70b9df2e73d325057b25b23723377596ee314","tid":2317053,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:41:46.000Z","msg":"【好鄰舍教會：10 警員搜觀塘會址　社工劉家棟稱被帶走助查】<br />\n<br />\n過往一直積極支持反送中運動的「好鄰舍北區教會」昨晚在 Facebook 發文指教會、堂主任陳凱興及其太太的戶口同時被滙豐凍結。今日教會再在 facebook 發文，指有 10 名隸屬毒品調查科&mdash;財富調查組的警員手持搜查令到該會觀塘聚會點，要求聯絡該會堂主任及公司董事以帶返警署協助調查。「好鄰舍北區教會」指警方有搜查物品，預備帶走部份信件。<br />\n<br />\n受聘於「好鄰舍北區教會」的註冊社工劉家棟及後在 Facebook 表示，現被警方帶走協助調查。劉家棟去年 7 月 27 日元朗衝突中被控阻差辦公罪成，判監 1 年，成為反修例事件中首名罪成判囚的註冊社工。他其後獲保釋等候上訴，再獲好鄰舍北區教會聘用。好鄰舍北區教會當時稱，是透過「被捕社工工作支援」成功眾籌約 70 萬元聘用劉家棟，劉於 9 月 1 日正式入職。<br />\n<br />\n今午五時，《立場新聞》記者於「好鄰舍北區教會」觀塘會址查看，裡面已關燈，亦無人應門。未知搜查行動是否已結束。<br />\n<br />\n相關報道：<br />\n<br />\n好鄰舍北區教會：遭滙豐凍結戶口　堂主任陳凱興夫婦戶口同被凍結　政治報復嚴重打擊宗教界<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/39RCDUQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F39RCDUQ&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W9AAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=51d80dca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/39RCDUQ</a><br />\n<br />\n與好鄰舍北區教會同遭凍結戶口　陳凱興透露一家留英：身無分文陷困境　憂不能回港<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/36TgaVr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F36TgaVr&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W9AAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=25e225d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/36TgaVr</a>"},{"pid":"42e0842eef01af691f2ae863b52fdf8728a41354","tid":2317053,"uid":57309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:42:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e3fc12948bafaf8df3e5d1b67e55fe11a43949","tid":2317053,"uid":15482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:51:14.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"acbd0c74c662265d4b1469f13ba843d622b8a78d","tid":2317053,"uid":181436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:03:43.000Z","msg":"見字幫推 觀塘重狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24feb5ba692fac575173a7008922183982a473ac","tid":2317053,"uid":181436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7340062af044462734b868194f172445999011d8","tid":2317053,"uid":181436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:04:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5b7297f262cfae4fd59723c8ba3e1e30920f0b","tid":2317053,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:04:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"809bb2ef0ebe229154db231afa5220046a0a3d13","tid":2317053,"uid":181436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4494139dfd66668397ab475809c6b2d01d5441","tid":2317053,"uid":181436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a5b7297f262cfae4fd59723c8ba3e1e30920f0b","tid":2317053,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:04:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:04:51.000Z","msg":"觀塘師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66311ba121c5cbfed465c194b88ec4bd318da3de","tid":2317053,"uid":181436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:05:09.000Z","msg":"開源道<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><